{"tid":1814790,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"如果你今日感到灰心，請入來取暖！","createTime":"2020-01-07T05:20:27.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-08T05:11:13.000Z","uid":70769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"aa0400527844c8bcc6ea2a9dce5a0c9d1c326ad2","tid":1814790,"uid":70769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T05:20:27.000Z","msg":"當你見到好多post 話退出<br />\n請你入來我地仲有好多人係度<br />\n<br />\n當你被人捉鬼感到灰心<br />\n請你入來我地仲有好多人開遮<br />\n<br />\n當你每晚懷疑自己孤獨<br />\n請你開窗，我仲每晚10點9叫緊<br />\n<br />\n當你覺得開始失民心<br />\n請你上facebook , 香港人仲未放棄<br />\n<br />\n當你覺得互屌好煩<br />\n去搵日程表，睇下來緊有咩活動參加<br />\n<br />\n當你唔想再勇武<br />\n先休息一下，繼續參加黃色經濟圈<br />\n<br />\n當你想鼓勵下大家<br />\n開多d正面post，推多d鼓勵post比人睇<br />\n<br />\n香港人仲未放棄，你不再年輕唔敢衝，唔敢打<br />\n請你而家用你ga方法鼓勵年輕人。<br />\n和勇不分唔係口號，係需要大家行動。<br />\n<br />\n冷氣同暖氣軍師要出來行動啦"},{"pid":"246dfa1712e00f593128e7737ab9dcec6af77962","tid":1814790,"uid":162008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T05:21:34.000Z","msg":"支持， 做實事，推日程，不放負！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n✴️HKVOTE Project 招募測試員✴️<br />\n------------------------------<br />\n👉🏻重點招募： ui, ux, security field 手足<br />\n👉🏻歡迎加入新改善建議Group: <a href=\"https://bit.ly/39fwrU9\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F39fwrU9&d=uPV0Czv%2B0bylLCB0p4n6nCEyVFbloTKGHdwbQdNTMZo%3D&h=932c7274\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/39fwrU9</a><br />\n<br />\n#一人一步支持手足<br />\n#快來高手指點<br />\n#齊齊做實事<br />\n#有其他Prj想搵人都可以聯絡Admin哦<br />\n<br />\n香港地投票 - 測試進行中（暫時勿發表高危議題<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.votes.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.votes.hk&d=uPV0Czv%2B0bylLCB0p4n6nCEyVFbloTKGHdwbQdNTMZo%3D&h=66d99cfa\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.votes.hk</a><br />\n香港人唔可以再慣性沉默，一起發聲，習慣投票表達意見吧"},{"pid":"2a3da2e7c3f02bdc3640888720e104fac965f525","tid":1814790,"uid":70769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T05:58:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oeQ6xfP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src